  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "四 “李氏将兴”还是“刘氏当王”",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300080660_8_2220-2250",
          "range": "2220-2250",
          "rangeStart": 2220,
          "rangeEnd": 2250,
          "markText": "不过也许我们的后人将来也会认为我们非常荒诞，这是历史的常态。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1729730285,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-10-24 08:38:05",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2250",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2250"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_7_5611-5707",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5611-5707",
      "markText": "君主太过精力旺盛，责任感太强，自我期许太高，都会给天下带来灾难。很多王朝实际上是毁灭在奋发有为的君主手里——他们觉得一万年太久，要只争朝夕，实际却四处树敌，臣民都被他们的理想所拖累，痛苦不堪。",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5611&rangeEnd=5707",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5611&rangeEnd=5707"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_3_527-576",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "527-576",
      "markText": "唐朝是中国文明的一个高峰，而之后的宋文明，虽然精致，却是一个长长的B浪反弹，酝酿着更大规模的下跌。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=576",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=527&rangeEnd=576"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_3_1360-1394",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1360-1394",
      "markText": "而粟特人却逐渐融入汉人之中，这或许是中国人善于做生意的部分基因来源。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1394",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1394"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_8_2220-2250",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2220-2250",
      "markText": "不过也许我们的后人将来也会认为我们非常荒诞，这是历史的常态。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2250",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2220&rangeEnd=2250"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_6_961-1000",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "961-1000",
      "markText": "中国人庆祝生日这一风俗便是受佛教的影响，而隋文帝也是中国第一个庆祝生日的皇帝。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=961&rangeEnd=1000",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=961&rangeEnd=1000"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_3_1809-1840",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1809-1840",
      "markText": "武则天正是在佛教繁荣的背景下，才能以佛教转轮王的身份登上皇位。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1840",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1809&rangeEnd=1840"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_6_5508-5540",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5508-5540",
      "markText": "所以是不是明君跟有几个女人真的关系不大，以私德评价人物难免狭隘。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5508&rangeEnd=5540",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5508&rangeEnd=5540"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_31_652-678",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "652-678",
      "markText": "同时开始制造舆论说高句丽在汉武帝时就是中国的一部分。",
      "totalCount": 112,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=652&rangeEnd=678",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=652&rangeEnd=678"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_8_550-726",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "550-726",
      "markText": "江都兵变的时候，叛军攻到大殿，杨广还跟萧皇后说：“得非阿孩邪？”意思是说，是不是齐王政变了。另外一边杨暕也被叛军抓住，以为是隋炀帝要杀自己，临死前还说：“诏使且缓，儿不负国家。”",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=726",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=550&rangeEnd=726"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_5_672-698",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "672-698",
      "markText": "洛阳被认为是宇宙的中心，被儒家学说赋予了神圣的属性。",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=698",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=698"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_7_5357-5443",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5357-5443",
      "markText": "隋炀帝的失败并不能归结于他政策方向的错误或是他个人品性的问题，主要的原因在于他施政的节奏太过猛烈，太过热切地期望早日重现历史上汉帝国的光辉，最终使帝国陷入了疲惫不堪的地步。",
      "totalCount": 99,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5357&rangeEnd=5443",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5357&rangeEnd=5443"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_8_1287-1338",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1287-1338",
      "markText": "任何专制政权，都必须一手持剑、一手布道，劝服被统治者相信它们代表的是神圣的力量、历史的趋势、正义的方向",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080660&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1287&rangeEnd=1338",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/a9d32fa0813ab8602g010f76?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1287&rangeEnd=1338"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080660_9_921-967",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "921-967",
      "markText": "读史书不但要看文本内容，还要看文本生成的背景，包括谁写的，设定的读者是谁，在什么背景下写的。",
